{"tid":1618272,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港鐵：籌備附例特勤隊工作已進入最後階段","createTime":"2019-10-04T05:09:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T05:54:07.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fe0f69cb4a727c155a755c92361278a109fe8928","tid":1618272,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T05:09:17.000Z","msg":"港鐵表示，在公眾活動前後多次有人違反附例逃票，籌備附例特勤隊的工作已進入最後階段，很快會詳細交代詳情。被問到是否希望招聘有警察經驗的人，港鐵車務總監劉天成沒有回應。<br />\n<br />\n至於港鐵有否安排警察進入車站休息，劉天成回應說，鐵路公司負責營運，鐵路治安要靠警方，過去幾十年這個做法持之以恆，大家目標一致，希望在大型公眾活動盡量提供列車服務，盡量保障乘客及職員安全。"},{"pid":"89b205adf267c0ba493c20590b86bc0d4a0acfdf","tid":1618272,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T05:09:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1484209-20191004.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1484209-20191004.htm&d=A2ufI7QLpLp1ny1o1CjT3i3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=a464368b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1484209-20191004.htm&h=105f2517\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1484209-20191004.htm</a>"},{"pid":"b5d81e142469c94240e9752cf3303c1ffa0afab2","tid":1618272,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T05:33:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17590cd28f405021df5ef8c7c53c48fb036b813b","tid":1618272,"uid":276989,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T05:40:34.000Z","msg":"鬥人多囉，反正都係圍毆"},{"pid":"a5a4450adfef93ccdec0b9d0832c3d8a6035fc0f","tid":1618272,"uid":171786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T05:54:07.000Z","msg":"被問到是否希望招聘有警察經驗的人<br />\n<br />\n係就好，唔使顧慮對方係唔係黃，仲有真狗都唔驚啦，何況只係有過做狗經驗"}]}